="https://www.nme.com/artists/bjork">比约克</a>宣布出版一本新书，该书将记录和记录她<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/bjork-cornucopia-london-the-o2-live-review-2577096">五年的“聚宝盆”巡演</a>- 了解更多信息如下。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/bjork-cover-interview-2022-fossora-3318517">比约克：“首先你创造一个有声音的宇宙，然后你进入它”</a></strong></li></ul><p> <em>《聚宝盆》：这本书</em>是对艺术家突破性的“聚宝盆”巡演的实体纪念，该巡演在过去五年中经历了多次迭代。</p><p>该书预计于 11 月 15 日发行——<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DA3fx52o5Fu/?img_index=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">现已开放预订</a>。该书长达 480 页，包含摄影师 Santiago Felipe 拍摄的 300 多张照片。 </p><figure id="attachment_3544513" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3544513" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3544513" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2023-Bjork-singer.jpg" alt="Björk（摄影：Santiago Felipe/Redferns for ABA）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2023-Bjork-singer.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2023-Bjork-singer-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2023-Bjork-singer-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2023-Bjork-singer-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2023-Bjork-singer-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2023-Bjork-singer-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3544513" class="wp-caption-text"> Björk（摄影：Santiago Felipe/Redferns for ABA）</figcaption></figure><p> Björk 在社交媒体上写到<em>《Cornucopia: The Book》</em> ：“在这次巡演之前，我花了十年时间在虚拟现实和动画领域使用 360 度声音和视觉软件，创作了第一张应用专辑《Biophilia》，以及后来的《Vulnicura》作为 VR 专辑。我受到完全沉浸式体验的想法的启发，在冰岛灯塔度过春天，将乌托邦传播到全环绕扬声器中。我的目的是将我们为 21 世纪 VR 创造的东西带入 19 世纪的剧院 - 将其从耳机带到舞台。”</p><p>她继续说道：“这一愿景是通过 27 个移动窗帘实现的，这些窗帘捕获不同纹理和 LED 屏幕上的投影，从而创建数字动画表演：现场音乐的现代灯笼魔术。我还想使用定制乐器：磁性竖琴、阿鲁风琴、圆笛和混响室，这些乐器是与音频建筑师专门建造的，以增强在个人教堂中最亲密的表演版本。”</p><p>除了记录“聚宝盆”之旅的奇观和技术细节之外，即将出版的书还增加了一个叙述：“在这个故事中，有一个次要情节：阿凡达的第二个故事——一个现代木偶，通过炼金术从木偶变异到木偶。 ，从心脏受伤到完全痊愈的状态。”</p><p>请查看下面 Björk 的完整公告。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DA3GjZENlJn/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,3