yle="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3763460" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/billie-eilish@2000x1270.jpg" alt="比莉·艾利什在舞台上表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/billie-eilish@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/billie-eilish@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/billie-eilish@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/billie-eilish@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/billie-eilish@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/billie-eilish@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3763460" class="wp-caption-text">比莉·艾利什.图片来源：阿图罗·霍姆斯/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>当被问及卡马拉承诺解决的与艾利什有关的问题时，这位年轻的音乐家回答道：“他真的是人权的忠实拥护者。非常支持妇女权利、妇女生殖权利、社会正义和枪支法。我的很多粉丝将第一次能够投票。所以我问，‘你喜欢自由吗？’第一位女总统？真的会很棒。作为一名女性，我希望在自己的国家感到安全。”</p><p>继上个月公开支持哈里斯之后，艾利什的《当派对结束时》最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilishs-when-the-partys-over-closes-kamala-harris-ad-on-reproductive-care-3795331">出现在民主党关于生殖保健的广告中</a>。</p><p>艾利什只是在即将到来的选举中表示支持哈里斯的众多音乐家之一。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-announces-endorsement-of-kamala-harris-for-president-3792514">Taylor Swift</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-john-legend-and-more-endorse-kamala-harris-for-us-president-3776745">Charli XCX</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonces-freedom-soundtracks-kamala-harris-first-presidential-election-campaign-video-3777987">Beyoncé</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-slams-those-avoiding-presidential-election-what-the-fuck-are-you-talking-about-3790934">Megan Thee Stallion</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-pnk-perform-what-about-us-with-daughter-to-close-